Feature: User Authentication

Background:
   Given the user has navigated to 'account' route

Scenario: A user can log in
    Given a user has an account
    When the user inputs the correct email address
    And the user inputs the correct password
    And the user clicks the login button
    Then the user will be logged in
    And the user will be redirected to the home page

Scenario: A user can create an account
    Given there is not already an accout associated with the provided email
    When A user input an email
    And the user inputs a password and confirmation password
    And the passwords match eachother and requirements
    Then the account is created
    And the user is logged in


Scenario: A user can log out
    Given a user is logged in
    When a user clicks 'log out'
    Then the user will be logged out